Results obtained from the full workﬂow are sketched for three COFs: 18041N3, 13180N3, and 05001N2. From the left to the right we
can ﬁnd the initial geometry, the energy proﬁle during the three-stage optimization, the ﬁnal geometry and its main geometric properties, the CO
